OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F378A1777468273
OL,3,CTwo boys killed in Wolverhampton house
OL,4,Cfire named
OL,6,FA one-year-old and three-year-old boy
OL,7,Fkilled in a house fire in
OL,8,FWolverhampton have been named as Xaliq
OL,9,Fand J'Saun.
OL,11,FIt's after officers were called to
OL,12,FMason Street at about 8:30pm on Friday
OL,13,F(24 April) along with the West
OL,14,FMidlands Fire Service and West
OL,15,FMidlands Ambulance Service.
OL,17,FFirefighters entered the property and
OL,18,Frecovered the two young boys but they
OL,19,Fwere pronounced dead at the scene.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G1/4
