PN,37802
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F378A1777468273
OL,3,CTwo boys killed in Wolverhampton house
OL,4,Cfire named
OL,6,FTwo other children and a woman were
OL,7,Falready out of the house before
OL,8,Femergency services arrived.
OL,10,FThey were checked over by ambulance
OL,11,Fstaff but did not need hospital
OL,12,Ftreatment and were discharged at the
OL,13,Fscene.
OL,15,FA woman in her 30s was arrested on
OL,16,FSaturday on suspicion of causing or
OL,17,Fallowing the death of two children.
OL,18,FShe has since been released on police
OL,19,Fbail.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G2/4
