CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F378A1777468273
OL,3,CTwo boys killed in Wolverhampton house
OL,4,Cfire named
OL,6,FWest Midlands Police said the family
OL,7,Fof the two boys have asked that their
OL,8,Fprivacy is respected as they come to
OL,9,Fterms with the tragedy.
OL,11,FOfficers are continuing with door-to-
OL,12,Fdoor enquiries with CCTV from the area
OL,13,Falso being retrieved and reviewed.
OL,15,FWest Midlands Fire Service said crews
OL,16,Farrived within five minutes of
OL,17,Freceiving reports.
