OL,3,CTwo boys killed in Wolverhampton house
OL,4,Cfire named
OL,6,F"Our thoughts are with the children's
OL,7,Floved ones and all those impacted by
OL,8,Fthis heartbreaking incident," the fire
OL,9,Fservice said.
OL,11,FAll Saints Church in Wolverhampton
OL,12,Fwill also open this evening for prayer
OL,13,Fafter the weekend's fire.
